Badges can be used as part of links or buttons to provide a counter.



Contextual variations:

Add any of the below mentioned modifier classes to change the appearance of a badge.

PrimarySecondarySuccessDangerWarningInfoLightDark

Pill badges:

the .badge-pill modifier class to make badges more rounded (with a larger border-radius and additional horizontal padding). Useful if you miss the badges from v3.

PrimarySecondarySuccessDangerWarningInfoLightDark

Links

the contextual .badge-* classes on an <a> element quickly provide actionable badges with hover and focus states.
